### Registro (primera vez con este email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Registro duplicado (mismo email — debe fallar con 400/422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

